SUMMARY:Quarterfinals Double Header
DTSTAMP:20260701T101455Z
DTSTART:20260711T143000Z
DESCRIPTION:Three days of quarterfinal madness wrap up tonight\, and the st
	akes couldn’t be higher. By the final whistle\, we’ll know our four semifi
	nalists. Don’t miss the moment it all becomes clear. \nKickoff for Game 1 
	is at 4:00 p.m. Kickoff for Game 2 is at 8:00 p.m. Admission is free! \nCo
	mmunity Partners: Further enhancing programming\, Levy Park will partner w
	ith local organizations to broaden community engagement\, including collab
	orations with cultural groups and soccer-focused nonprofits. Levy Park is 
	seeking enthusiastic volunteers and community partner organizations to hel
	p bring this festival to life. Volunteers will work directly alongside our
	 event team\, supporting booth operations and helping ensure every guest h
	as an unforgettable experience. Email us to learn more about volunteer opp
	ortunities. \nFood and Beverage Concessions: Enjoy a variety of festival f
	ood fare\, beer and wine\, and non-alcoholic beverages from Coca-Cola. \nM
	erchandise: Event merchandise celebrating Houston\, Levy Park\, and the gl
	obal soccer tournament will also be available for purchase. \nArt Installa
	tions and Photo Opportunities: Commemorate the experience with a photo tou
	r of the park\, including life-sized soccer-themed photo backdrops and a t
	ournament bracket. Visit our soccer ball music box and turn the crank for 
	festive sounds.\n\nhttps://www.levyparkhouston.org/events/quarterfinals-do
	uble-header/\n\nFrom Levy Park Houston
URL:https://www.levyparkhouston.org/events/quarterfinals-double-header/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:levy-park-houston
CATEGORIES:Levy Park Houston
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT9H
END:VEVENT
